  npcTalking: You
  _lines:
  - all patients are subject to a body examination to begin the rest of the admission
    process.
  - this is for the safety of everyone here.
  - but you're lucky, the director has only made the searches mandatory up until
    the bottom of the shoulder blades.
  - once we're in the examination room, please remove all articles (jewelry, clothing,
    etc.) within that area.
  - (the director is looking to distinguish Figures from normal human patients)
  - (Figures have "rendering anomolies", mutations of normal flesh)
  - (wonder what that looks like...)
